  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, you have honed your skills to such a point you introduce finesse into attacks that others would have been too busy focusing on their technique to execute properly. When you would cast a jutsu as a <em><strong>Finisher</strong></em> and reduce a creature to 0 hit points you may make a ranged weapon attack, once per turn. Additionally, you gain a +1 bonus to your Taijutsu Save DC.</p><p>Finally, once per rest when you would be targeted by an attack you may initiate a clash with a bukijutsu that has a casting time of no longer than one action, as a reaction. If the triggering jutsu or attack does not have the clash keyword you gain advantage on the clash check. Additionally, your jutsu is counted as being one rank higher than your opponents and   when you would lose a clash check you may spend 2 hit die to ignore the effects of losing a clash.</p>",
